*bareos-13.2.4-r1 (05 May 2015)

  05 May 2015; Marc Schiffbauer <mschiff@gentoo.org> bareos-12.4.5-r1.ebuild,
  -bareos-13.2.3-r1.ebuild, -bareos-13.2.4.ebuild, +bareos-13.2.4-r1.ebuild,
  bareos-14.2.1.ebuild:
  Rename USE sqlite3 to sqlite, revbump 13.2.4. Fixes #548648.

  08 Apr 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> bareos-12.4.5-r1.ebuild,
